OL,3,CPlans for new Jersey health department
OL,4,Cindependent from government
OL,6,FJersey's Health Minister has outlined
OL,7,Fplans to restructure the island's
OL,8,Fhealth system by creating a standalone
OL,9,Fdepartment which operates
OL,10,Findependently.
OL,12,FThe Government published the Health
OL,13,Fand Care Services Division Annual Plan
OL,14,Ffor 2025 on 14 January, with Deputy
OL,15,FTom Binet describing the sector as
OL,16,Fbeing at a "crossroads" as Jersey is
OL,17,Ffour years away from a new hospital
OL,18,Fbeing built at Overdale.
