OL,3,CPlans for new Jersey health department
OL,4,Cindependent from government
OL,6,FThe Minister's vision for an "all-
OL,7,Fencompassing, unified" system includes
OL,8,Fcreating a Jersey Health and Care
OL,9,FPartnership Board which would be
OL,10,F"separated from, but connected to"
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,FIt would aim to bring together all of
OL,14,Fthe island's health providers,
OL,15,Fincluding primary care, community
OL,16,Fcare, public health, government
OL,17,Fservices and the charitable sector to
OL,18,Fcoordinate and create better-
OL,19,Fintegrated services.
