OL,3,CPlans for new Jersey health department
OL,4,Cindependent from government
OL,6,FThe plans would effectively mean
OL,7,Fbringing the Government's varying
OL,8,Fhealth and social care functions under
OL,9,Fone umbrella, with a Chief Executive
OL,10,Fappointed to oversee the planning and
OL,11,Fdelivery of the joined-up services.
OL,13,FThe report also includes a proposal to
OL,14,Fchange the law where the Health
OL,15,FMinister would be responsible for the
OL,16,FGovernment's annual health and care
OL,17,Fservices budget and the Health
OL,18,FInsurance Funds, which mainly support
OL,19,Fprescriptions and GP services.
