OL,3,CPlans for new Jersey health department
OL,4,Cindependent from government
OL,6,FSummarising the plans, he wrote: "It
OL,7,Frecognises Jersey's unique position as
OL,8,Fa wealthy island with a dedicated
OL,9,Fworkforce and improving healthcare
OL,10,Ffacilities, suggesting that with
OL,11,Fappropriate investment and a
OL,12,Fwillingness to embrace change, Jersey
OL,13,Fcould become a model of best practice
OL,14,Fin health care.
OL,16,F"This plan aims to provide a
OL,17,Fcomprehensive overview of the proposed
OL,18,Fchanges, and the strategic direction
OL,19,Fneeded to achieve a unified,
OL,20,Fefficient, and effective health system
OL,21,Ffor Jersey."
