OL,3,CPlans for new Jersey health department
OL,4,Cindependent from government
OL,6,FThe report's proposals are part of the
OL,7,Fisland's Common Strategic Policy 2024-
OL,8,F2026, started in May last year, which
OL,9,Faims to find "practical solutions to
OL,10,Fmake islanders' lives better".
OL,12,FWithin the policy are plans to tackle
OL,13,Fconcerns about rising health spending,
OL,14,Falongside ideas to deal with the
OL,15,Fconsequences of an ageing population,
OL,16,Ffalling birth rates and growing
OL,17,Fnumbers of islanders with disabilities.
