OL,3,CPlans for new Jersey health department
OL,4,Cindependent from government
OL,6,FPart of the Common Strategic Policy
OL,7,F2024-2026 involves delivering health
OL,8,Fand care services across a range of
OL,9,Fsites including the Enid Quenault
OL,10,FHealth and Wellbeing Centre at Les
OL,11,FQuennevais, the Samares Ward at St
OL,12,FEwold's Residential Care Home, a new
OL,13,Facute hospital at Overdale, an
OL,14,Foutpatients facility in St Helier and
OL,15,Fa 'Health Village' in St Saviour.
